data.description: Welcome to the charming 4 bedroom 3 full bath home at 10906 Bristle Oak Dr. Inside, the cedar stairway offers a warm welcome and rustic charm. The practical downstairs guest bathroom features a walk-in shower and access to the garage. The kitchen showcases granite countertops, a versatile island bar, and brand-new 2022 Frigidaire appliances. The pantry is unique in design and has a sink and washer/dryer connection. This is an all-electric home. The backyard boasts a large concrete area for entertainment, complete with TV access and a bar. You'll love the mini orchard with lime, peach, pecan, fig, orange, grapefruit, & mandarin trees, all set against mature oaks. Two storage sheds offer additional outdoor storage. Inside, the bedrooms provide ample storage. The master suite has a spacious walk-in closet and a large bathroom with a walk-in shower and two vanities. Each bathroom has convenient closet space. The well-maintained A/C, a roof replaced in 2019-2020, a 3-year-old water heater, and recently updated wood blinds ensure comfort and efficiency. The back porch, offering approximately 800 square feet of covered space, is ideal for outdoor relaxation, featuring a bar and TV connections.  Explore the comfort and charm of 10906 Bristle Oak Dr, a well-appointed home waiting for you!
